 This relationship between consumption and social mobility itself is an
 idea that dates back least as far back as Adam Smith 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "SmithMoralSentiments"

\end_inset

 and has been re-evaluated by modern economists in the recent decades 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "FrankPond,GalbraithAffluent,GalbraithEssential,HirschSocialLimits"

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

